# To-Do List Web App

A simple and modern **To-Do List** web application built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. This app allows users to add, remove, and manage tasks in a clean and interactive interface.

---

## Features

- Add tasks to your to-do list.
- Remove tasks individually.
- Press **Enter** key to quickly add tasks.
- Clean and responsive UI with CSS styling.

---

## Technologies Used

- **HTML** – Structure of the app
- **CSS** – Styling and layout
- **JavaScript** – Dynamic functionality and interactivity

